.TH "LIGHTNING-PEER-LOCAL-PCT-MAX" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-peer-local-pct-max \- FEAT-2508 peer with highest local balance percentage
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning peer-local-pct-max
.SH DESCRIPTION
peer-local-pct-max for lightning CLI (FEAT-2508).
.PP
Returns the peer ID and local balance percentage for the channel with the highest local-to-total ratio.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
